Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 29 June, 2024

1. Introduction

Welcome to the KR Agency app, developed by Travancode Software Tech Private Limited ("we," "our," "us"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner.

2. Information We Collect

We collect the following personal information when an account is created by the admin for employees:

Name
Age
Phone number
3. Purpose of Data Collection

The personal information collected is used for the following purposes:

To create and manage user accounts for employees.
4. Data Sharing

We do not share your personal information with any third parties.

5. Data Security

We implement various security measures to protect your personal information, including:

Requiring an access token for API calls.
Login authentication using phone number and password.
6. User Rights

As an employee, you can request access to, update, or delete your personal information offline through the admin. The admin is your employer and can facilitate these requests.

7. Data Retention

We retain your personal information for as long as you are employed by the company. Once your employment ends, your personal data will be deleted.

8. Third-Party Services

Our app does not use any third-party services that collect data.

9. Changes to This Privacy Policy

Any changes to this privacy policy will be communicated to you offline via a company circular.

10. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy or our data practices, please contact us at:

Travancode Software Tech Private Limited
travancodecompany@gmail.com
